{"tid":2358153,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"特斯拉Model Y長續航版美國降價近2000美元","createTime":"2021-01-08T02:37:42.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-08T03:18:15.000Z","uid":295230,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"84248ffaa20c30197820243dc83738dfe96dcef3","tid":2358153,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T02:37:42.000Z","msg":"特斯拉Model Y後驅長續航版在美國的售價有所下降，當前其售價為4.8萬美元，此前售價為4.99萬美元，降價幅度為0.19萬美元。<br />\n<br />\n1月1日，Model Y在中國開售，車輛來自該公司位於上海的超級工廠。2020年底前，特斯拉完成了上海工廠二期工程的建設，新廠房專門用於Model Y的生產。年底的報道顯示，特斯拉已經開始在工廠內生產Model Y。在上市之後，這款純電動跨界車受到了中國消費者的歡迎，原因是其起售價格比預期低了16萬，僅33.99萬元。<br />\n<br />\n在開售之後，特斯拉中國網站由於湧入大量訂單，甚至一度出現了崩潰的情況。昨天的報道稱，龐大的需求讓特斯拉難以招架，當前官網上的預計交付日期已經延長到了今年第二季度。<br />\n<br />\n特斯拉在美國銷售的Model Y生產自該公司位於加利福尼亞州弗裏蒙特的超級工廠。此外，該公司目前還正在德國柏林和美國德克薩斯州建設新工廠。"},{"pid":"a25dad04cefdb61a4156e10fa863ecd4f8e3767b","tid":2358153,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T02:38:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"801c4f6f9eadb471d0973ec365f1e0117a748147","tid":2358153,"uid":370972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T02:38:57.000Z","msg":"Tesla hits $9000"},{"pid":"4698b6bd5ab25ba2030d9ac6bb51197bb360b9ad","tid":2358153,"uid":24833,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T02:39:50.000Z","msg":"賣唔去先要減價，跌撚死你班仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6dae3dc2acef7aaffab453b2451e57ac01f91491","tid":2358153,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T02:40:09.000Z","msg":"同場消息︰<br />\n<br />\nTesla發佈 Model Y Standard Range 版本及 7座位版本<br />\n<br />\nTesla launched the seven-seat option for the Model Y, alongside a new Standard Range Rear-Wheel Drive variant, in its online configurator. The new entry-level Model Y trim is available for $41,990 before incentives, and the seven-seat option is available as a $3,000 option.<br />\n<br />\nThe Tesla Model Y Standard Range RWD features 244 miles of EPA-estimated range, a top speed of 135 mph, and a 0-60 mph time of 5.3 seconds.<br />\n<br />\nAs noted by the electric car maker, the Model Y&rsquo;s seven-seat interior includes the following: third row seating for two, easy entry into the third row, third row USB-C charging, sliding second row with adjustable seatbacks, fold-flat second and third rows for maximum cargo storage, and electronic fold-flat releases in the trunk."},{"pid":"39a3431f9dde3791262b494ff43f494d3156a371","tid":2358153,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4698b6bd5ab25ba2030d9ac6bb51197bb360b9ad","tid":2358153,"uid":24833,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T02:39:50.000Z","msg":"賣唔去先要減價，跌撚死你班仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T02:41:03.000Z","msg":"除左減價外，仲有新型號既Model Y發佈<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2edd608fb6a3278c8cbbdbf009673eb92bb46daf","tid":2358153,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"801c4f6f9eadb471d0973ec365f1e0117a748147","tid":2358153,"uid":370972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T02:38:57.000Z","msg":"Tesla hits $9000"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T02:41:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\"